INSERT INTO `TRAITS` (`TRAIT_ID`, `TRAIT_DESC`, `BOOK`, `PAGE`) VALUES
(1, 'I idolize a particular hero of my faith and constantly refer to that person\'s deeds and example.', 'Online', 0),
(2, 'I can find common ground between the fiercest enemies, empathizing with them and always working toward peace.', 'Online', 0),
(3, 'I see omens in every event and action. The gods try to speak to us, we just need to listen.', 'Online', 0),
(4, 'Nothing can shake my optimistic attitude.', 'Online', 0),
(5, 'I quote (or misquote) the sacred texts and proverbs in almost every situation.', 'Online', 0),
(6, 'I am tolerant (or intolerant) of other faiths and respect (or condemn) the worship of other gods.', 'Online', 0),
(7, 'I have a joke for every occasion, especially occasions where humor is inappropriate.', 'Online', 0),
(8, 'Flattery is my preferred trick for getting what I want.', 'Online', 0),
(9, 'I\'m a born gambler who can\'t resist taking a risk for a potential payoff.', 'Online', 0),
(10, 'I lie about almost everything, even when there\'s no good reason to.', 'Online', 0),
(11, 'Sarcasm and insults are my weapons of choice.', 'Online', 0),
(12, 'I keep multiple holy symbols on me and invoke whatever deity might come in useful at A given moment.', 'Online', 0),
(13, 'I always have plan for what to do when things go wrong.', 'Online', 0),
(14, 'I am always calm, no matter what the situation. I never raise my voice or let my emotions control me.', 'Online', 0),
(15, 'The first thing I do in a new place is note the locations of everything valuableor where such things could be hidden.', 'Online', 0),
(16, 'I would rather make a new friend than a new enemy.', 'Online', 0),
(17, 'I am incredibly slow to trust. Those who seem the fairest often have the most to hide.', 'Online', 0),
(18, 'I don\'t pay attention to the risks in a situation. Never tell me the odds.', 'Online', 0),
(19, 'The best way to get me to do something is to tell me I can\'t do it.', 'Online', 0),
(20, 'I blow up at the slightest insult.', 'Online', 0),
(21, 'I know a story relevant to almost every situation.', 'Online', 0),
(22, 'Whenever I come to a new place, I collect local rumors and spread gossip.', 'Online', 0),
(23, 'I\'m a hopeless romantic, always searching for that \'special someone\'.', 'Online', 0),
(24, 'Nobody stays angry at me or around me for long, since I can defuse A amount of tension.', 'Online', 0),
(25, 'I love a good insult, even one directed at me.', 'Online', 0),
(26, 'I get bitter if I\'m not the center of attention.', 'Online', 0),
(27, 'I\'ll settle for nothing less than perfection.', 'Online', 0),
(28, 'I judge people by their actions, not their words.', 'Online', 0),
(29, 'If someone is in trouble, I\'m always willing to lend help.', 'Online', 0),
(30, 'When I set my mind to something, I follow through no matter what gets in my way.', 'Online', 0),
(31, 'I have a strong sense of fair play and always try to find the most equitable solution to arguments.', 'Online', 0),
(32, 'I\'m confident in my own abilities and do what I can to instill confidence in others.', 'Online', 0),
(33, 'Thinking is for other people. I prefer action.', 'Online', 0),
(34, 'I misuse long words in an attempt to sound smarter.', 'Online', 0),
(35, 'I get bored easily. When am I going to get on with my destiny.', 'Online', 0),
(36, 'I believe that everything worth doing is worth doing right. I can\'t help itI\'m a perfectionist.', 'Online', 0),
(37, 'I always want to know how things work and what makes people tick.', 'Online', 0),
(38, 'I\'m full of witty aphorisms and have a proverb for every occasion.', 'Online', 0),
(39, 'I\'m rude to people who lack my commitment to hard work and fair play.', 'Online', 0),
(40, 'I like to talk at length about my profession.', 'Online', 0),
(41, 'I don\'t part with my money easily and will haggle tirelessly to get the best deal possible.', 'Online', 0),
(42, 'I\'m well known for my work, and I want to make sure everyone appreciates it. I\'m always taken aback when people haven\'t heard of me.', 'Online', 0),
(43, 'I am utterly serene, even in the face of disaster.', 'Online', 0),
(44, 'The leader of my community has something wise to say on every topic, and I am eager to share that wisdom.', 'Online', 0),
(45, 'I feel tremendous empathy for all who suffer.', 'Online', 0),
(46, 'I\'m oblivious to etiquette and social expectations.', 'Online', 0),
(47, 'I connect everything that happens to me to a grand cosmic plan.', 'Online', 0),
(48, 'I often get lost in my own thoughts and contemplations, becoming oblivious to my surroundings.', 'Online', 0),
(49, 'I am working on a grand philosophical theory and love sharing my ideas.', 'Online', 0),
(50, 'My eloquent flattery makes everyone I talk to feel like the most wonderful and important person in the world.', 'Online', 0),
(51, 'The common folk love me for my kindness and generosity.', 'Online', 0),
(52, 'My favor, once lost, is lost forever.', 'Online', 0),
(53, 'If you do me an injury, I will crush you, ruin your name, and salt your fields.', 'Online', 0),
(54, 'I watch over my friends as if they were a litter of newborn pups.', 'Online', 0),
(55, 'I place no stock in wealthy or wellmannered folk. Money and manners won\'t save you from a hungry owlbear.', 'Online', 0),
(56, 'I feel far more comfortable around animals than people.', 'Online', 0),
